    <section>
        <p>At <strong>Yaarishhh</strong>, we respect your privacy and understand that you may want to delete your account at any time. If you wish to permanently delete your <strong>Yaarishhh</strong> account, please follow the steps outlined below:</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>
        <p>To request the deletion of your <strong>Yaarishhh</strong> account, please follow these steps:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Contact Us via Email:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Send an email to <em>yaarishhh212@yaarishhh.com</em> with the subject line <em>"Request to Delete Account"</em>.</li>
                    <li>In the body of the email, mention your request to delete your account and provide the registered email address associated with your account.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Phone Support:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Contact us directly via phone at <em>+91 8088687360</em> for assistance with the account deletion request.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Important Notes</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Permanent Deletion:</strong> Once your account is deleted, all data associated with it, including personal information, transaction history, service details, and any other records, will be permanently erased from our system. This action is irreversible.</li>
            <li><strong>Outstanding Balances:</strong> Ensure that any outstanding balance or pending subscriptions are settled before requesting account deletion. Any unpaid dues will be lost once the account is deleted.</li>
            <li><strong>Subscription Cancellation:</strong> If you have an active subscription, it will be canceled upon account deletion. No further charges will be applied after the deletion request is processed.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Processing Time</h2>
        <p>Your account deletion request will be processed within <em>7 business days</em> from the time of receipt. You will receive a confirmation email once your account has been deleted.</p>
    </section>

