        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Certain data may still be retained for legal, regulatory, or business purposes as required by law, even after account deletion.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Reactivation</h2>
        <p>Once your account is deleted, it cannot be reactivated. To use the <strong>Yaarishhh</strong> app again, you would need to create a new account.</p>
